"ड्रॉप डाउन बॉक्स</link></emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An item in the <link linkend=\"visualdict-drop-down-box\">Drop Down Box</"
"link> that has been selected"
msgstr ""
"एक आइटम<link linkend=\"visualdict-drop-down-box\"> ड्रॉप डाउन बॉक्स</link> जिसे "
"चुना गया है"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
